TO SU ZAIZAI, FROM ZHANG LULI

7
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:31,640
<i>It has been a while, Zaizai.</i>

8
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:33,440
{\an8}<i>I can't use my phone anymore</i>

9
00:01:33,520 --> 00:01:35,040
{\an8}<i>as the NCEE is around the corner.</i>

10
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,720
<i>I can only write letters instead.</i>

11
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,480
<i>I was on the phone with Lurang
a while back.</i>

12
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,040
<i>He was in a good mood</i>

13
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,400
<i>and told me a lot about you guys.</i>

14
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,600
<i>I don't know anyone else.</i>

15
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,640
<i>But from the way he talked about them,</i>

16
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:49,680
<i>they must be just as interesting as you.</i>

17
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:53,120
<i>You said Lurang became friends with you</i>

18
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,680
<i>because you kept bothering him.</i>

19
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,800
<i>Let me tell you in secret.</i>

20
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:58,480
<i>I've seen Lurang play</i>

21
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,440
<i>with that toy many times.</i>

22
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:03,120
<i>He must be happy to have you as a friend,</i>

23
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,600
<i>but won't admit it.</i>

24
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,680
<i>My brother is cute in that way.</i>

25
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,560
<i>By the way,</i>

26
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:11,080
<i>I talked to my parents after I got back.</i>

27
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:13,280
<i>I get the feeling they're slowly changing.</i>

28
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,560
<i>I hope things get better.</i>

29
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:20,200
<i>Zaizai, I wish you all the best too.</i>

30
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,600
Zaizai!

31
