You're going to be late for school!

32
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,400
I'm coming!

33
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,240
THE FIRST HIGH SCHOOL

34
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:38,000
You used to be excited about your birthday

35
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,360
before it even arrived.

36
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,120
Why don't you want to celebrate this year?

37
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:45,000
I know there are some things

38
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:46,400
that I can't avoid,

39
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:49,400
but I can't help but think about the fact

40
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,840
that my birthday
is before the winter break.

41
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:53,640
After my birthday,

42
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:55,480
Zhang Lurang will go back to Suyang.

43
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:57,800
I suddenly don't feel like celebrating it.

44
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,360
It's exactly because he's leaving

45
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:03,040
that we must enjoy your birthday

46
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,320
so that it's meaningful.

47
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,240
We must have a good time.

48
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,720
Come on.

49
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,000
This is so difficult.

50
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,760
What is so difficult about buying a gift?

51
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,440
Winter is coming.

52
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:21,280
You can buy a scarf or gloves.

53
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,240
Or...

54
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,480
Bracelets are nice too.

55
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,680
Most girls like pretty things.

56
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:30,840
Do you?

57
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:38,360
Are you asking that question

58
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:42,640
to mock me for not being like most girls?

59
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,880
Forget it.

60
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,920
There is no use

61
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,080
keeping it after buying it.

62
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,880
I got this from the spicy hot pot event

63
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,160
at the canteen.

64
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,760
I have no use for it. You can have it.

65
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,160
No.

66
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,680
Knowing Jiang Jia's personality,

67
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,520
she'll wait outside the canteen tomorrow.

68
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,120
I found this on the roadside.

69
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,200
I'm lucky, aren't I?

70
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:02,080
That is too fake.

71
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,960
Gu Ran.

72
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,040
Guilty conscience? You look spooked.

73
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,600
What do you want with me at this hour?

74
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:14,280
Well,

75
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,080
it's just that

76
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:20,720
I just bought Su Zaizai's birthday gift.

77
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:22,600
It's one of those carved wooden dolls.

78
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,680
Don't you know her better?

79
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,120
What do you think?

80
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,800
Sure, Zaizai will probably like it.

81
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:29,960
Is that all?

82
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,840
Yes. What else could there be?

83
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,680
By the way,

84
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,760
the store where I bought the gift

85
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,360
happened to have a promotion,

86
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,480
buy 2 and get 20% off,

87
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,920
so I was suckered into buying this.

88
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,000
I have no use for it,

89
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,440
so I guess you can have it.

90
00:05:46,880 --> 00:05:47,920
If you don't want it...

91
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,760
Why would I turn down something free?

92
00:06:02,760 --> 00:06:05,680
You don't like me, do you?

93
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,400
Who did you say I like?

94
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,160
You?

95
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:15,320
How is that possible?

96
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,440
What is so good about you?

97
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:19,080
Besides having big eyes,

98
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,280
fair skin, a small face,
curly lashes, and tall,

99
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,640
what qualities do you possess?

100
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:33,160
I...

101
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,840
What I meant is that

102
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,920
you're not really my type.

103
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,520
Don't overthink it.

104
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:47,680
That is good.

105
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:49,680
I thought you had a thing for me.

106
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,680
That scared me.

107
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,360
Don't flatter yourself.

108
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:14,200
We finally made it to the Friday
without evening self-study.

109
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,320
We're leaving first.

110
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,960
-Bye.
-See you next week.

111
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,960
Let's go.

112
00:07:22,040 --> 00:07:23,760
Let's go get Zhang Lurang and Gu Ran.

113
00:07:23,840 --> 00:07:24,800
Dinner is on me today.

114
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,640
I've even decided on the restaurant.

115
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,600
If you're treating us,

116
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,120
we might make you broke.

117
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,200
I'm happy because it's my birthday.

118
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,680
Su Zaizai, Mr. Lin wants to see you.

119
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:43,280
I wonder what it is about.

120
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:45,160
Why don't I text you the address?

121
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,320
Head there first. I'll catch up with you.

122
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:48,840
Okay, then we'll leave first.

123
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,080
Okay.

124
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,760
Sir.

125
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,160
Mr. Lin, you wanted to see me?

126
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,000
It's no big deal.

127
00:08:00,080 --> 00:08:01,880
Grade 10 just had their monthly exam.

128
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:04,040
They're eager to get their English scores.

129
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,680
I don't have enough graders,

130
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:07,320
so I wanted to ask for your help.

131
00:08:07,400 --> 00:08:08,800
Grade the multiple-choice questions

132
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,200
using this answer key.

133
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:13,760
It won't take long.

134
00:08:13,840 --> 00:08:15,280
Are you

135
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,240
in a hurry to leave?

136
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:18,280
I'm not in a hurry.

137
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:19,880
Okay.

138
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:23,120
Then you can grade at that table.

139
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:24,080
Here.

140
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:26,960
Thank you.

141
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,960
Are you done?

142
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,320
Goodbye, Mr. Lin.

143
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,360
Thank you so much for today.

144
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,080
Be careful on your way home. Bye.

145
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,160
<i>It's late.</i>

146
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,600
<i>Why don't you guys go home first?</i>

147
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:06,040
<i>What? I guess we have no choice.</i>

148
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,840
<i>We'll celebrate your birthday tomorrow.</i>

149
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:12,200
<i>It's fine. We can do it anytime.</i>

